      "role": "user",
      "content": "i tried moving the caliper and it seems to move okay but that noise is still there and it's really weird. it’s like this sudden screeching that comes and goes for no reason. is there any chance it's just an intermittent electrical issue or some kind of internal glitch in the brake system itself?",
